### ============================
### Room API (read-only)
### ============================

### List all rooms
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/rooms
Accept: application/json

### Get a room by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/rooms/room-hall-a
Accept: application/json

### Get a non-existent room → expect 404
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/rooms/does-not-exist
Accept: application/json

